Metadata-Version: 1.0
Name: radioplayer
Version: 0.1
Summary: A little radio player
Home-page: http://base-art.net
Author: Philippe Normand
Author-email: phil@base-art.net
License: GPL2
Download-URL: http://base-art.net/static/radioplayer-0.1.tar.gz
Description: 
        A simple python radio player
        
        Currently supports only FIP and FranceInter.
        
        Dependencies:
        
        - pynotify
        - python-dbus
        - gst-python
        
        Features:
        
        - notifications of song with libnotify
        - scrobbling to lastfm and/or librefm
        - optionally dump the stream to a local file
        - multimedia keys support (stop, playpause)
        - IM message status update (pidgin, gajim, telepathy)
        
Keywords: radio,multimedia,gstreamer,telepathy,d-bus,libre.fm,last.fm
Platform: UNKNOWN
Classifier: Development Status :: 5 - Production/Stable
Classifier: Environment :: Console
Classifier: Operating System :: OS Independent
Classifier: Programming Language :: Python
